242,243,244,245],"Supplementum epigraphicum graecum, 1923-","Korhonen, 2004, IMusCatania","Libertini, 1930, Il Museo Biscari","Ferrua, 1938, Osservazioni sulle iscrizioni cristiane catanesi","Noy, 1993, Jewish inscriptions of Western Europe","Korhonen, 2001, Osservazioni sul collezionismo epigrafico siciliano",[247,248,249,250,251,252],"F2GG87EQ","2EUC82DH","SKUU2R8X","BPRRV8SB","IBA4JMAN","CVTW89H4",[254,255,256,25,30,34,257,258,259,260,258,261,262,125],"isic003290","epitaph for priska(?)",{"_":5},"catina","catania","italy","sicily","museo civico di catania","ancient greek",[],{"title":265,"body":266,"divs":267,"editions":294,"images":313,"handnote":319},"ISic003290. Epitaph for Priska(?)","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πρῖσκα\">[Πρ]ῖσκα\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">[ἔζ]ησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">[ἔτ]η\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"δέκ\n                    αοκτῶ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"δέκαοκτῶ\">δέκ-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[αοκ?]τῶ\u003C/span>´ 🕎 \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πρῖσκα\">Πρῖσκα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"δέκαοκτῶ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"δέκαοκτῶ\">δέκαοκτῶ\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πρῖσκα\">[..]ΙΣΚΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">[..]ΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">[..]Η\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"δέκ\n                    αοκτῶ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"δέκαοκτῶ\">ΔΕΚ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[...]ΤΩ\u003C/span>🕎\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πρῖσκα\">ΠΡΙΣΚΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"δέκαοκτῶ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"δέκαοκτῶ\">ΔΕΚΑΟΚΤΩ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003290_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003290_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003290.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003290-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>Ferrua, Noy: [---]ις κα[---]; Korhonen: [Πρ]ῖσκα\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Libertini, Korhonen: [ἔζ]ησεν; Ferrua, Noy: [---]ης εν[---]\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 3\">line.3: \u003Cspan>Liberini, Noy: δέκ[α]; Ferrua [---]ηδε κ[---]; Korhonen: [ἔτ]η δέκ[α]\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 4\">line.4: \u003Cspan>Ferrua: ἐτω(ν); Korhonen: [ἐν Χρισ]τῷ (the space between τω and the previous letter could be justified if we suppose an abbreviation: ἐν Χρ(ισ)τῷ); Chaniotis: [μήνας ὀκ]τώ\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 4\">  \u003Cspan>Ferrua, Noy and Korhonen 2001 interpreted the symbol as a menorah, but later Korhonen as a palm\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Prisca lived for 18 (?) years.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Prisca visse per 18 (?) anni.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph is Jewish, as revealed by the symbol of a menorah. Korhonen rejects the Judaic provenance of the inscription believing the symbol to be a palm, but the feet of the menorah seems to be present even if not rubricated. Korhonen’s supplement to l. 4 \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐν Χρ(ισ)τῷ\u003C/span> (the same abbreviation as in RQUA 10 (1896) 38 nr. 67), for this reason, cannot be supported: moreover, the space does not seem sufficient. If one assumes that a few characters are missing on the right, the integration of Chaniotis (ap. SEG) \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[μήνας ὀκ]τώ\u003C/span> is also not possible. One possibility would be to integrate the numeral \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">δεκαοκτώ\u003C/span>. For the name Prisca in another Latin inscription from Catania from the imperial period, see CIL 10.1088*199 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003241\" target=\"_blank\">ISic003241\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 51.1200 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1930 318 no.8 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1938 72 no.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Noy 1993 no.147 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2001 93-94 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001425\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001425\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 192 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> \u003Cp>A with broken bar, Δ with serif, lunate Ε and Σ, cursive Ω.\u003C/p> Lines 1-4  18-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[268,271,274,277,280,282,285,288,291],{"id":269,"html":270},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πρῖσκα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πρῖσκα\">[Πρ]ῖσκα\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">[ἔζ]ησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan clas